### UTIL-API-001 | HTML-PDF 파일 렌더링 및 변환
### Markdown source: docs/03_API/PHASE2_API_SPEC.md
### Endpoint: POST /api/gen/docs/{repo_id}/export/pdf
### 관련 기능 ID: DOCS-UTIL-B-201
### 상태: 시작 전 (Phase 2)
### ============================================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = replace-me
@repoId = 3f7cc46e-d954-83ab-9f12-013b0c9d2a1e

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/gen/docs/{{repoId}}/export/pdf
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/pdf

{"theme":"default","includeCodeHighlight":true}

### 200 OK — binary response
### Content-Type: application/pdf
### Content-Disposition: attachment; filename="{repoName}_onboarding.pdf"
### theme: default | dark | minimal
### 오류: 401 UNAUTHORIZED, 404 REPO_NOT_FOUND, 404 DOCS_NOT_FOUND, 500 PDF_RENDER_FAILED
